# 6789f4c9b87049f68e8f6803eb2e87c3
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:23
msgid "Structure"
msgstr ""

# 9b0c7e53197f4bbcb9210c67acdb46e1
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:25
msgid ""
"The |ATS| documentation is presented as a single manual, sub-divided into"
" the following sections:"
msgstr ""

# 569612a96fd74e9e80df6d2520ea026b
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:33
msgid "Preface"
msgstr ""

# 7f0b8b72bb17466eb58817a0df0d1a1c
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:29
msgid ""
"The introductory section to the manual as a whole, with a brief "
"exposition on |TS| and its general role in a network and application "
"infrastructure. The typographic conventions used in the manual should be "
"covered here to ease readers' comprehension of the following sections, as"
" well as pointers to additional resources available outside of the "
"manual."
msgstr ""

# 67555d7841e34cb8ae7b512da4003041
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:38
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr ""

# 24af8e7eb6b043f1b0958c1bc30ab537
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:36
msgid ""
"Aimed at administrators and developers new to |TS| who wish to install "
"and configure a |TS| instance in the least amount of time necessary, "
"without delving into the full featureset or the internals of the |TS| "
"architecture."
msgstr ""

# d8a53bf7a2b347cab57d049a0531123f
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:44
msgid "Administrator's Guide"
msgstr ""

# bf6307c5bd93420e8b65e4ea82b65822
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:41
msgid ""
"Provides in-depth coverage of all |TS| features and configurations for "
"use by administrators responsible for installing, configuring, and "
"maintaining |TS| instances. Troubleshooting, performance tuning, and "
"plugin usage should all be covered in this section of the manual."
msgstr ""

# ede33ba68fda413bac9936fa217b0560
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:48
msgid "Developer's Guide"
msgstr ""

# 4428a6a322724e4496942442f7a8cccd
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:47
msgid ""
"Documentation of internal |TS| architecture as well as guides on plugin "
"development and debugging are presented in this section."
msgstr ""

# 8a3ddb568c8140619f64699e6060bca3
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:54
msgid "Appendices"
msgstr ""

# b48a813eb9ab4a968a93f489ecf4be3d
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:51
msgid ""
"Glossary, common references to both administrator and developer guides "
"(such as status code tables and command line utility usage), frequently "
"asked questions, and errata should all be located in this final section "
"of the manual."
msgstr ""

# 26208ae6eed84482b50d7aaaef3272e1
#: ../../developer-guide/documentation/structure.en.rst:56
msgid ""
"Within each top-level section, a short introduction should be provided to"
" the content of that section, as well as a brief note on the intended "
"audience. A very high level treatment of each chapter should be presented"
" to allow readers to more easily locate the most relevant chapters for "
"their current needs."
msgstr ""

